AI in Sports

LaLiga's AI Integration: Spain's LaLiga has incorporated AI into its core strategy, utilizing predictive analysis and algorithms to enhance match analysis and media production. This integration aims to boost team competitiveness and reshape fan engagement. ​
Reuters

Advancements in AI Models

Google's Gemini 2.5: Google released Gemini 2.5, a reasoning model designed to pause and "think" before providing responses. This model represents a shift towards integrating advanced reasoning capabilities into AI systems. ​
