Alibaba's Qwen2.5-Omni-7B: Alibaba introduced "Qwen2.5-Omni-7B," an AI model optimized for smartphones and laptops. Capable of handling text, images, audio, and video inputs, it is designed to run on edge devices and is open-sourced on platforms like Hugging Face and GitHub. ​
